<p class="ql-align-justify">胆大包天，敢惹猫老大…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201111/d94d296e5e98490baa5a57e8e1ab7a3a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
